      "order_number": 0,
      "text": "Hey."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 109.76,
      "start_time": 108.7,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 1,
      "text": "All righty."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 112.06,
      "start_time": 110.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "3ef09720-9f18-4605-820d-d55101152f97",
      "order_number": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, I wonder how Drake mess that up."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 114.42,
      "start_time": 112.84,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't his fault."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 121.5,
      "start_time": 114.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "It was Corey had made some account changes, ownership changes this week and none of us like picked up on it."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 124.73,
      "start_time": 121.51,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "So that makes sense is what is, um,"
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 127.45,
      "start_time": 126.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "I'm making you the host right now."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 127.81,
      "start_time": 127.46,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "Ok."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 128.45,
      "start_time": 128.32,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "Cool."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 131.51,
      "start_time": 128.64,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "A little bit of prep and context that might be helpful."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 133.83,
      "start_time": 131.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "There are two companies."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 138.25,
      "start_time": 133.84,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "It might be a weird situation of um two different management companies over two different regions."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 144.44,
      "start_time": 138.26,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "I'm not sure a O reality and ism, so I would just ask about that."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 145.18,
      "start_time": 144.79,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Yeah,"
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 149.57,
      "start_time": 146.24,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "I think it makes sense for you to run it and then to pass it off to John afterwards."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 151.04,
      "start_time": 149.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "So it's not like I don't need to be here."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 151.61,
      "start_time": 151.05,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "You know what I mean?"
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 152.3,
      "start_time": 151.88,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "id": "96ff2cc2-f427-4a53-9317-829e004c4e67",
      "recording_id": "2bc02067-fabe-456b-8b0b-3b59efd5d738",
      "end_time": 154.52,
      "start_time": 152.95,
      "recording_attendee_id": "e8a7a2db-aa48-44d4-a544-ecb0977d6444",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "But um, all right, brother."
